<p class="">Those warnings from below the Gangway are at the back of me and <span id="656" class="column-number" data-column-number="656"></span> the warnings from the other side of the House are in front of me, and I place a correct value on both of them. I cannot at the moment answer the Question with regard to the amount of sterling without looking into it but when a country like Burma, having been controlled by another, seeks her independence and obtains it, I think that a little tolerance and care are essential to get matters working right, and I propose to exercise them. If in the end it is proved that the trust we have placed in them to carry out their obligations is not fulfilled, our policy must accordingly change.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
